overview.en: Txt is a decentralized Finance (defi) platform, which aims to establish aggregate liquidity pool, leverage trading platform, automatic market making, and other functional platforms. It obtains the highest profit output in contract trading interaction by rebalancing data. Txt token can be used for platform governance. Members of airbitclub in more than 200 countries around the world can dig out t ecological public chain mother currency by locking up the warehouse TXT, open all the landing applications of T ecology, and create a blockchain version of Alibaba.
overview.zh: TXT是一个去中心化金融(DeFi)平台，其旨在建立聚合流动性池，杠杆交易平台，自动做市，及其他功能型平台，它通过重新平衡数据得出合同交易互动中的最高利润产出。TXT代币可被用于平台治理，遍布全球200多个国家的ＡirbitClub 成员可以通过锁仓TXT去挖出T生态公链母币，开启T生态的全部落地应用，打造区块链版的阿里巴巴。
